quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  10,21,"Futhi kwathi lapho sizwisa khona abantu umusa emva kokuba sebethintwe ukuhlupheka kwaba yilapho bona benzela khona izimpawu ethu amacebo, ithi uMvelinqangi oshesha ngokwedlulele ekwenzeni amacebo ngempela izithunywa zethu (izingelosi) ziyakubhala phansi lokho enikucebayo"
  10,22,"Nguyena owenza ukuthi nikwazi ukuhamba ezweni nasolwandle kuze kuthi uma nina nisemikhunjini ihamba nabo kushaya umoya omnandi bakuthokozela lokho, kwafika isivunguvungu somoya kwafika kubona namagagasi aqhamuka kuzona zonke izindawo futhi bacabanga ukuthi ngempela bona babezungeleziwe base bememeza (bethandaza) kuMvelinqangi ngobuqotho, ingeyakhe inkolo (bathi), “uma usisindisile kulokhu ngempela siyoba ngababongayo”"
  10,23,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho esebasindisile kwaba yilapho bona benza okungalindelekile ezweni okungesilona iqiniso, Oh Bantu! Ukungalaleli kwenu (uAllah) kungukuzilimaza nina uqobo, kuphela kuyinjabulo yempilo yalomhlaba, kukuthina ukubuyela kwenu ngakho-ke siyonitshela ngalokho enanikwenza"
  10,24,"Kuphela ukufana kwempilo yalomhlaba kunjengamanzi (imvula) esiwehlisela phansi evela esibhakabhakeni emilisa izitshalo zomhlaba abadla kuzona abantu nezinkomo kuze kube yilapho umhlaba uphenduka ohlobisekileyo nobukeka umuhle futhi abantu abahlala kuwona bacabanga ukuthi bona banamandla kuwona, kufike kuwona impoqo yethu ebusuku noma emini, sawenza ukuthi ube ngowezivuno (ukuhamba kwesikhathi) kube sengathi awuzange uchume izolo kanjalo siwachaza ngobunjalo bawo amavesi kubantu abacabangayo"
  10,25,Futhi uMvelinqangi unimemela ekhaya lokuthula futhi uholela lowo amthandayo endleleni eqondileyo
  10,26,"Okwalabo abenze okuhle (umvuzo) omuhle kakhulu nokungaphezulu kwalokho futhi angeke kubekhona ubumnyama nakudumazeka okuyomboza ubuso babo, labo-ke bangabangane besivande bona bayohlala khona ingunaphakade"
  10,27,"Futhi labo abenza imisebenzi emibi umvuzo womsebenzi omubi uyalingana nawo futhi ukudumala kuyobamboza angeke babenomvikeli ovela kuMvelinqangi, kuyoba sengathi ubuso babo bumbozwe ngamakhekheba obumnyama bobusuku labo ngabangani bomlilo bona bayohlala khona ingunaphakade"
  10,28,"Nangosuku lapho sibaqoqela ndawonye bonke bese sithi kulabo ababekhonza izithixo (hlalani) endaweni yenu nina kanye nezithixo zenu (enanizikhonza) ngakho-ke siyobe sesiyabahlukanisa izithixo zabo ziyothi, “nina naningasikhonzi thina”"
  10,29,"Ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi wanele njengofakazi phakathi kwethu naphakathi kwenu, uma nanisikhonza (ukusikhonza) kwenu sasingakunakile"
  10,30,Lapho-ke yonke imiphefumulo iyolingwa bese (iyazi) lokho eyayikwenza ngaphambilini futhi iphindiselwe (imiphefumulo) kuMvelinqangi umvikeli wayo weqiniso futhi okwabadukela yilokho ababekuqamba